{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1566524, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得体育锻炼多消耗的食物，水，防疫成本可以忽略不计，对医疗资源更可能是减少消耗吧。。。", "timestamp": 1619773847, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566525, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "锻炼对健康负收益？？", "timestamp": 1619773862, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566532, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz一家人基本都是业余运动员，身体都有运动损伤", "timestamp": 1619773932, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566536, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "跟工人比也完全没道理吧，这是不同的社会分工啊。体力劳动者消耗体力，脑力劳动者消耗脑力，后者要特意运动来进行一定的体力消耗，那前者不也得特意动脑来进行脑力消耗吗。。", "timestamp": 1619773993, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566537, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": 1566532, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 严格讲那是训练，不是对一般人而言的锻炼。", "timestamp": 1619773998, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566541, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "而且dz见了好多因为练跑步成绩伤到膝盖的", "timestamp": 1619774058, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566543, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": 1566532, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这又不是体育运动的锅。。有多少人运动的强度能达到损伤身体的地步啊。。", "timestamp": 1619774073, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566550, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": 1566541, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 好多不等于大多数，锻炼不等于追求跑步成绩，伤到膝盖不等于【比起不锻炼】消耗了更多医疗资源。", "timestamp": 1619774193, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566637, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": 1566550, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 有道理 希望运动给大多数人带来的是正收益", "timestamp": 1619774972, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566640, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "运动会不就是一群需要锻炼的人看一群需要休息的人运动", "timestamp": 1619774993, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566652, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": 1566640, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 真讽刺啊", "timestamp": 1619775060, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566666, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "唉，很多体力劳动者的工作环境很恶劣，比如建筑工人，钢厂工人，我看到他们的工作环境真的很心疼，他们以后肺出问题的概率比我们大的多。\n环境好的体力劳动者还是少", "timestamp": 1619775163, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566699, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "体力劳动之所以体育劳动是因为有报酬。如果你也去做体力劳动，劳动力价格会降低。这是社会分工所致。做好自己即可。", "timestamp": 1619775659, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566705, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": 1566532, "tag": null, "text": "业余运动员啥意思？", "timestamp": 1619775700, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566733, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就是学校、单位的球队、田径队", "timestamp": 1619776153, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1566745, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 308104, "reply_to": 1566733, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有时候会和dz有同感（", "timestamp": 1619776286, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 308104, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "锻炼的时候看见工人常常感到惭愧\n为什么我们要特意运动，而更多人要承担过量的体育劳动呢\n似乎体育锻炼要占用过多的社会资源（食物、水、医疗资源、防疫成本）而对健康很可能是负收益\n大家怎么看清华的体育传统呢（脱胎于贵族传统还是军事化传统）", "timestamp": 1619773622, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1619776286, "url": "", "vote": {}}}